Package nusri.fyp.demo.controller

Class ConfigController

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.controller.ConfigController
@RestController @RequestMapping("/config") public class ConfigController extends Object
This controller provides endpoints for managing the configuration of the system.
It supports functionality for getting and updating the configuration of various services,
including the Python server, Roboflow, and other model-related configurations.
It exposes the following operations:
  • Retrieve all configurations
  • Update all configurations
  • Update Python server host and port
  • Update Roboflow server host and port

This controller is responsible for interacting with the ConfigService to retrieve and persist configuration values.
